In re Resignation of Clauder.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Clauder (1994), 70 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 94-1576 Submitted and decided July 28, 1994.)

The resignation of Michael Arthur Clauder of Cincinnati, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0031987, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
